summary: An ordinance relating to the Diagonal Avenue, et al. Trunk Sewer System, as contemplated by Resolution No. 15713; providing for the construction of sections of the storm and sanitary portions of said Trunk Sewer System; appropriating money therefor from the Seattle Sewer Bonds 1946 Fund; and providing that said appropriation shall be charged to funds which may hereafter be appropriated in aid of the local improvement district proposed to be created, pursuant to Resolution No. 15713.
